usage: alert_quality.py [-h] --prometheus PROMETHEUS
                        [--alertmanager ALERTMANAGER] [--period PERIOD]
                        [--tenant TENANT] [--json] [--markdown] [--ci]
                        [--min-score MIN_SCORE]

Alert Quality Scoring — analyze Alertmanager history to identify problem
alerts

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --prometheus PROMETHEUS
                        Prometheus URL
  --alertmanager ALERTMANAGER
                        Alertmanager URL (for suppression data)
  --period PERIOD       Analysis period (default: 30d)
  --tenant TENANT       Filter to specific tenant
  --json                JSON output
  --markdown            Markdown output
  --ci                  CI mode: exit 1 if any BAD alert
  --min-score MIN_SCORE
                        CI minimum score threshold (default: 0)
